Package com.pandora.calculation.services

Class TransportCalculationServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.calculation.services.TransportCalculationServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
TransportCalculationService
@Service public final class TransportCalculationServiceImpl extends Object implements TransportCalculationService
Implementation of the TransportCalculationService interface that calculates the transport of chemical species within a simulation.

This implementation utilizes a service for retrieving configuration information about chemical species, and computes the transport rates based on the species' properties and the current state of the simulation represented by the variables y and the pandoraTimestep.

Instances of this class are intended to be managed by the Spring framework as Spring beans, allowing for dependency injection of required services.
